content:
Easily Update Context Tags

Use the Assignment element in a pricing procedure to set and change the context tag values of variables. Give your users the flexibility to customise a variable's value within a pricing procedure and enable their business to optimise their pricing strategies for maximum effectiveness.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.
title: Easily Update Context Tags in Salesforce Pricing
